---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Medication List Tool – KindScript" 
  description="Prepare a clear, printable list of your current medications and supplements to bring to medical visits."
>
  <div class="section">
    <h1>💊 Current Medications</h1>
    <p>This tool helps you prepare a medication list to bring to medical appointments. You can list prescription meds, OTC items, and supplements — and then copy, print, or download it.</p>

    <h2>🔍 What this tool is</h2>
    <p>This is a writing tool to help you or a loved one keep track of medications, vitamins, and supplements. It’s helpful for medical visits, hospital stays, or anytime someone might ask what you're taking.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>🔒 <strong>Private by design</strong><br />Everything you type stays on your device and never gets sent anywhere — no servers, no databases, no tracking. Your information is processed entirely in your browser.</li>
      <li>🩺 <strong>Not medical advice</strong><br />This is a writing tool to help you advocate for yourself or a loved one. It isn’t a substitute for professional medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>🛠️ Ready to fill it out? <a href="#medication-form">Jump to the form</a></p>

    <hr class="tool-divider">

    <h3>📝 Example output</h3>
    <pre class="output-box">
Name: Jamie R.
Date: 2025-08-01
Medication List
Medications: Zyrtec 10 mg (once daily)
Supplements: Vitamin D, Magnesium</pre>

    <hr class="tool-divider">

    <div class="section tool-form" id="medication-form">
      <div class="form-inner">
        <form>
          <label for="name">Name (optional)</label>
          <input type="text" id="name" placeholder="e.g. Jamie R." />

          <label for="date">Date</label>
          <input type="date" id="date" />

          <div class="form-section-label">💊 Medications</div>
          <div id="medications"></div>
          <div style="margin-top: 0.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">
            <button type="button" id="add-medication" class="btn subtle">
              + Add another medication
            </button>
          </div>

          <label for="supplements" class="form-section-label">🌿 Supplements</label>
          <textarea id="supplements" placeholder="e.g. Vitamin D, Magnesium"></textarea>

          <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 1rem;">
            <button type="button" id="generate-btn" class="btn dark">✨ Generate Medication List</button>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="tool-divider">

    <h2>📋 Generated Medication List</h2>
    <p>You can copy, print, or hand this to your provider — whatever works best.</p>
    <div id="output" class="output-box" contenteditable="true" role="textbox" aria-label="Generated medication list">
      (Fill out the form and click Generate)
    </div>
    <div class="button-group">
      <button type="button" id="copy-btn" class="btn dark">Copy to Clipboard</button>
      <button type="button" id="print-btn" class="btn dark">Print This</button>
      <button type="button" id="download-btn" class="btn dark">Download as .txt</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="margin-top: 3rem;">
    <a href="/tools">← Back to all tools</a>
  </div>

  <script src="/js/medication-list.js" defer></script>
</BaseLayout>
